```plantuml
@startuml yoshixmk_remarks

actor User
participant "Chrome Extension" as ChromeExt
participant "Web Server (Deno)" as Server
participant "FaunaDB" as FaunaDB
participant "GitPress Blog" as GitPress

User -> ChromeExt : Clicks remark button
ChromeExt -> Server : POST /api/remarks (remark data)
Server -> FaunaDB : Execute GraphQL mutation (createRemark)
FaunaDB --> Server : Remark created
Server --> ChromeExt : Success response

User -> Server : GET / (homepage)
Server -> FaunaDB : Execute GraphQL query (getRemarksCount)
FaunaDB --> Server : Remarks count
Server -> FaunaDB : Execute GraphQL query (getRecentRemarks)
FaunaDB --> Server : Recent remarks
Server -> User : Render homepage with count & remarks

User -> Server : GET /trip (travelogue)
Server -> GitPress : Fetch RSS feed
GitPress --> Server : Travelogue content
Server -> User : Render travelogue page

@enduml
```